&lt;/h2>&lt;p>Linux is the foundation of most server systems, containers (Docker, Kubernetes), and cloud platforms. DevOps professionals need to master Linux to:&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>‚úÖ Manage servers effectively.&lt;/li>
